      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeb no ta wiſſa / par ko\nwiſch nepateefi ſwehrejs/ to pa-\nſchu buhs winnam wiſſai atdoht/\nun to peektu Dalku pahr to pee-\nlift/ tam/ kam tas peederr/ buhs\nwinnam to doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winnam buhs tam\nKUNGAM faru Noseedsibaſ-\nUppuri atneft/ weenu Annu/ kaſ\nbes Wainas/ pee ta Preceſtera/ no\nta Gannama-Pulka pehz tawas\nNospreeschanas / par Noseedsi-\nbaſ-Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs tam Preceſteram\npar to Salihdsinaſchann darriht\npreekſch ta KUNGA / tad tas\nwinnam taps peedohts/ par jeb-\nkuru no wiſſa/ ko wiſch darra/\nceekſch ka tas noseedſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tas KUNGS run-\nnaja us Motsu/ un faz-\nzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pawehti Aäronam un win-\nna Dehleem/ un fakſi : Schi irr\nta Dedſama-Uppura Bauſliba /\nfchun Dedſanam-Uppuram buhe\nus to Altari wiſſu Naſti degt\nlihs Rihtam/ un ta Altara ug-\nguns degs us winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam Preceſteram buhe\nfawas linnu Drebbes uſwiſſt /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs wi\nwas Drebbes iſwiſſt/\nDrelybes apwiſſt / un\nbuhs tobs Pelnus no Le\nra isneft kahdá fchtihſta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu to Uggi\nAltari buhs us to eed\ntam ne buhs iſdſihſtam\ntam Preceſteram buhs\nifrihtu Malku eededſin\nwiſnam buhs us to /\nun Uppuri lift/ un us\nteikſchanas Uppuru Ta\ndſinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Uggunſlai\nus to Altari degg/ tan\ndsift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schi nu irr ta\nUppura Bauſliba/ Aär\nleem buhs to uppureb\nta KUNG A us t\nPreekſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un weenaim bu\nfawu Sanju pillu xen\nEhdaina-Uppura Kwce-\nteem/ un no winna E-\nwiſſu to Wihraku/ kas\ndamn-Uppuri irr/ tad\nnam to eededſinaht us\nta irr weena falda &\npar winna Peemi\npreekſch ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to / kas no t\nbuhs Aäronam un wi\n"
    }
  ],
